entries.tt8l18: Return when you are ready to serve Jabba.
entries.tt8l16: No. I am not ready, yet.
entries.tt8l14: I am TT-8L. If you wish audience with Jabba the Hutt, I can ask inside the palace if anyone has work for you.
entries.tt8l13: This is the Palace of Jabba the Hutt.  It is not open to the public. If you wish to enter, you must first complete tasks for Jabba and his associates.
entries.tt8l12: Wait here. I will inquire if anyone inside needs any minor tasks done by the likes of one such as yourself.
entries.tt8l11: Jabba does not mingle with tourists. Perform errands for Jabba and he may grant you audience.
entries.tt8l8: I am here to offer my services.
entries.tt8l7: I want to see Jabba the Hutt.
entries.tt8l6: Bib Fortuna will speak with you now. Go find him inside.
entries.tt8l5: There are no appointments currently scheduled with Imperials. Go away.
entries.tt8l4: Your kind is not welcome here.
entries.tt8l2: There is more work to be done. Are you ready for another mission?
